    "scope_boundary": "IN: Update `angular.json` to use `@angular-devkit/build-angular:application` for SASS, adjust any custom Webpack or builder configuration that references the old sass‑loader, run the SASS import deprecation ADR checks, and execute the full UI test suite to verify no regressions. OUT: The broader Angular 19 framework upgrade (core, router, RxJS), backend services, data‑access layer, and any non‑UI components are out of scope for this ticket.",
